nodes.text: Webb was a male Human living on Tatooine during the Cold War. In 3643 BBY he was affiliated with Andronikos Revel, a pirate who hid in a private room of the Siltshift cantina in Mos Ila, and served as his means of contact with outside world.
Webb appears in Star Wars: The Old Republic during the Sith Inquisitor class mission on Tatooine.
